              <span>테마</span>
            </a>
          </li>
        </div>
        <div class="cell">
          <li>
            <a href="#">
              <img>
              <span>헤어 관리를 위한 트리트먼트</span>
              <span>찰랑거리는 머릿결을 위하여</span>
              <span>테마</span>
            </a>
          </li>
        </div>
        <div class="cell">
          <button class="btn_more_info">더보기(1 / n건)</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    <section class="hot_category">
      <div class="hot_category__title">
        <h2>지금 뜨는 테마 카테고리<h2>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel_container">

      </div>
      <div class="footer"></div>
    </section>
    <script type="module" src="/javascripts/index.js"></script>
